{"tid":1292123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有五毛開 tg group 呃巴打入去","createTime":"2019-07-07T07:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:28:26.000Z","uid":39752,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3098f5ba7605c51b93cb2ccc8463d5bd196e97","tid":1292123,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"佢哋會用啲大家好有興趣吹水嘅話題開 post，例如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">買過個島</span></strong><br />\n表面上寫咗篇千字文，想邀請大家入去繼續討論<br />\n<strong>但係大家留言去問一啲實作嘅質疑點，佢哋就絕對唔會回應，即使啲嘢公海都講得</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當你提醒佢有相同性質嘅 group 做緊 / 質疑點解要開過個新</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢就會發矛屈你係五毛</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被人屌到差唔多或者推唔郁，又會即刻開過個新 post<br />\n自然會有其他巴打（包括 CD-ROM）淨係睇到頭 po 就俾佢呃咗入去</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291396</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291398</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291865</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291973</a><br />\n<strong>（以上全部係同一個 account <span style=\"color: red;\">Timothy #30561</span>）</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一同佢講方舟計劃有二千幾人做緊，佢就發矛話方舟嗰邊二千幾人都係五毛<br />\n理據係「六年前舊登做相同計劃被五毛搞散」呢啲不可驗證嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種情況完全超出咗各有各做嘅合理懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得 account 可以 hack 可以買賣，過往表現同埋會員編號都不可作參考<br />\n注意自己 tg 加密（唔 show 電話／唔用慣用 username）先好入啲公海 group</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8bbb74306240ce03a1185da637395520cb18